{{DISPLAYTITLE:A_FireGoldWandPL2}}
'''A_FireGoldWandPL2'''<br>
(''no parameter'')<br>

Fires five hitscan attack dealing 1d8 damage in a fan going through 2.8125° steps from -5.625° to 5.625°, using a {{Class|GoldWandPuff2}} and fires two {{Class|GoldWandFX2}} projectiles, one at -5.625° and the other at 5.625°. In addition, it plays the sound "weapons/wandhit" on the WEAPON channel.

This codepointer is restricted to {{Class|GoldWandPowered}} and derived classes.

